  metadata.xml:
  Version bump to latest release.

  29 May 2012; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> -gmt-4.0.ebuild,
  gmt-4.5.6.ebuild:
  Stabilise 4.5.6 on amd64 and x86 and remove older.

  12 May 2012; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> gmt-4.5.6.ebuild:
  Fix double prefix install

  10 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> gmt-4.5.6.ebuild:
  Fix dodoc call. Fixes bug #370805.

  07 Jun 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> gmt-4.5.6.ebuild:
  Make triangle configure optional. Thanks to Donnie for spotting.

